{"id": "1454108976307503225", "channel_id": "1454108976307503225", "type": 0, "author_id": "233217233583734785", "author_name": "lavache.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Context:\nIn light of the crit rate bug in Sunfall, I wonder if any other crit sources might have issues?\n\nIssue:\nIt is quite hard to view and test since there are many wheels (e.g. Lily's wheel) and covs (e.g. Paradox ) that only give crit to command cards or just a subset of them.\n\nQuestion:\nWould it be possible to display final crit rates per command card? (and even the final dmg including crit dmg if possible) \n\nSuggestions:\nAt a minimum, just a crit rate % next to the dmg amount shouldn't add to the text clutter too much? e.g. instead of \"Deal X DMG\", it could say \"Deal X DMG, with Y% Crit rate\"; or even better, \"Deal X DMG, crit for Z DMG at Y%\"\n\n(probably a separate discussion on how to improve/toggle detailed text per card)\n\nIn addition, exalts and tentacle crit rates could be more visible too, might also just an extra number next to their dmg which are already shown in UI.", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T13:49:55.990000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-26T16:51:50.452000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "❌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454108976307503225", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Display crit rate (and maybe final dmg if crit) per card?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1454105786015023195", "channel_id": "1454105786015023195", "type": 0, "author_id": "233217233583734785", "author_name": "lavache.", "author_bot": false, "content": "I really like radios dramas, but took me a long while to realise they were there! being buried quite a few layers into the archives, and I wonder if many other players don't even know they exist like me.\n\nIt would be nice to make them more obvious, especially when new ones are released; perhaps Event tag is a good place to prompt and link players to them?", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T13:37:15.365000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454105786015023195", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Link new Radio Dramas in Event tag when they are released", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
